Package: toponym
Title: Generates Maps Of Specific Or Frequent Toponyms
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lennart", "Chevallier", email = "mail@lchevallier.de", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Søren", "Wichmann", email = "wichmannsoeren@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Author: Lennart Chevallier [aut, cre],
        Søren Wichmann [aut]
Description: A simple package for visualizing toponym distributions. You either provide a regular expression searching for places matching it or find the most frequent toponyms specific to one area.
